	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65021649"><p>It's a bit like moving to the cloud... We had a sysadmin managing our colocated rack servers, anything you asked him was done within the day. A new CTO brought his guys to move us to to the cloud (the old sysadmin quit as they were put above him). Yes, there are advantages with the cloud setup, but we somehow suddenly need 3 cloud engineers minimum to keep up! Well, we have 2 actually, but they definitely can't keep up...</p></div>
	</div>

